<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Cat Gear Index and its structured approach to cat supplies research.">
  <article class="article-shell">
    <h1>About Cat Gear Index</h1>
    <p class="lead">Cat Gear Index is a structured database for comparing cat supplies by practical ownership factors: fit, cleaning, recurring cost, materials, maintenance, and product limitations.</p>
    <p>The site is intentionally built around tables, tools, and buyer guides instead of vague product roundups. Our goal is to make product research easier for new cat owners, multi-cat homes, and small-apartment households.</p>
    <p>Cat Gear Index does not provide veterinary diagnosis, treatment advice, or emergency guidance. For health, diet, medication, or behavior concerns, contact a licensed veterinarian.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
